description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 7

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

Group Two is introduced and the program heads back to NSW where newlyweds Uel and Shannelle take to the kitchen. Love began through cooking but will the magic last in an instant restaurant?
